data.description: Sixty-four beautiful acres of country views with 46 shares of irrigation, a 3 bedroom 2 bath home with 3 garages , small shed, Three phase electricity (a HUGH PLUS) There is a pond with irrigation ditches running through the property. Perfect for all kinds of livestock and/or animals, or just a buffer from the rest of the world! Minutes from Navajo State Park for boating, fishing, water fun, hiking, etc. Also 25 minutes from La Plata Airport , Sky Ute Casino, Shopping and More!  Plenty of room to store your toys. THIS REALLY IS A MUST SEE!!! So much potential for the right buyer.
